{"tid":346133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 有冇方法唔要腳甲？","createTime":"2017-08-03T16:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T17:13:40.000Z","uid":66740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e985b1be65c40650cf8d4aee80c0e0fb441e11b3","tid":346133,"uid":66740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:23:40.000Z","msg":"我自己隻腳趾公腳甲特別大塊，每一次做運動，跑步、行山都會頂到隻鞋。<br />\n唔關對鞋/對襪既事，我試過晒點樣都會頂腳指公，原因真係太大塊同生得太出，<br />\n所以我次次腳甲都會頂到成塊黑晒有魚血係入面，痛到仆街，最後成塊甩出黎我先得到解脫。<br />\n有冇巴打知點樣可以令到腳甲唔再生出黎？"},{"pid":"7dfea867b518d1b55f3f12c3d65516799ace4dbd","tid":346133,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f198e541d7a3e4c17d4c27e549709dd951c405cc","tid":346133,"uid":88805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:26:24.000Z","msg":"義趾"},{"pid":"00aef94bcadb1b1636f8ba3c5393ffe2f04c021b","tid":346133,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"斬腳趾"},{"pid":"b95f0fda33c87f2380e631fb1ab491ebda139bcf","tid":346133,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:33:22.000Z","msg":"每晚臨訓前啜十分鐘腳趾甲，半個月左右 佢就會停止生長"},{"pid":"8322f1d5bfa146f102e1affbd0137757c14726d7","tid":346133,"uid":93218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"剪趾甲喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec6791f21355f214cc50b80f53261c40d501ea0","tid":346133,"uid":127611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:50:31.000Z","msg":"著腳趾鞋"},{"pid":"37a229e017841518f8e1b2b835512737e02820bc","tid":346133,"uid":133363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T16:56:59.000Z","msg":"It can be removed permanently...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(warning)<br />\n<a href=\"https: